            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Trahius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex cert="low">aetor</ex></expan> AP<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="2"/>de stipe <expan><abbr>idemq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> cavi<supplied reason="lost">las<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Z. 1: pr(aefectus) oder pr(aetor), Ap[ollini templum?] bzw. Ap[ollinensium templum?] - Caballos Rufino, Ap[ollini] - Gil. - Z. 2: cavi[las d(e)? s(ua)? p(ecunia)? f(aciendas)? c(oeravit)?] - Gil, ähnlich Caballos Rufino. - Reduzierter Text in AE 1987. (C): Mosaik aus republikanischer Zeit.</p>
            </div>
